GET http://localhost:5001/api/medical-documents?search=blood&patient_id=9897

### Scenario 4: Filter by Category
GET http://localhost:5001/api/medical-documents?category=lab_results&limit=20

### Scenario 5: Get Recent Uploads
GET http://localhost:5001/api/medical-documents?sort_by=uploaded_at&sort_order=desc&limit=10
